      <title>I'm makeing this post in hopes someone at SOE will listen</title>
      <link>http://eqforums.station.sony.com/eq/board/message?board.id=Stormhammer&amp;message.id=1980#M1980</link>
      <description>&lt;div&gt;I have been on Legends off and on since its release Feburary after Luclin was launched.  My first character then was Dabrix a level 55 epic human monk.  I was from Lanys and ended up running into one of Lanys's top monks while I was there, Sarthis who taught me a few things.  Since then I have been on the server about every other month.  Yes I was a Day 1 person but I have not been here full time like Phaed or Tharkis.   But on 4 different accounts and about 10 characters  I put my time and a ton of my money's worth in it since I was useing 2 accounts at the same time while I was here.  I have come here to comment on the issue of people being able to go to Firiona Vie. &lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt; &lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;I am sure no one that works for SOE will listen to this and take me seriously but I will give it a shot.  From what I have heard , and Im sure other people have too, a lot of people might be considering quitting the game all together after the server is brought down.  I myself came here only for the GM events.  Some of my charaters were  Dundada, Venicore (3 times) Tweadle, Tweedlebot, Dabrixx was here 3 times also hehe, Tilluian, and Gombaah most recently. &lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt; &lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;I never even managed to get these guys any real levels as I capped off around 55 on a few and with Gombaah 59.  With the help of a few people here I was able to complete Tweadle's Mage epic in about a week, which i think is a new record for a mage epic hehe. I also did Gombaah's shaman epic in about the same time thanks to Denon's army helping me in Fear and help from Phaed, Spriggan and Spriggin on my final battles in City of Mist. I really came here for the events.  They were the most fun I have ever had in this game being a guy that played since  pre-kunark.  I tried to make all 3 events a day and therefore my leveling suffered greatly as was evident when after I transfered off I made it to 64 in only 4 days with Gombaah being on my new server.  Down to my point.  Right now Gombaah and Tilluian are sitting on 7th Hammer because Lanys has always been my true home server even though most of the characters I grew up with EXPing  Alnaraon, Ralanon, Cuukey, Mezzah, Keadre, Gothor, Kamakuk, Dondor and many other old schoolers  have moved on I returned there to continue my fun. &lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt; &lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;The problem is both Gombaah and Tilluian were both created Firiona Vie.  Alot of their gear is from zones they are 5-10 levels away from entering from expansions I dont even have yet and some drops are raid loot because they were created on Firiona Vie and thus bought all of it in the bazzar. &lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt; &lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;I am making this post to argue for Legends characters being able to transfer to the Firiona Vie server.  In the rules it specificaly states that no character shall transfer off of the firiona vie server yet I have two on the on Seventh Hammer proudly displaying my &amp;quot;of Firiona Vie' tags.  Since I was able to move my characters off of Firiona Vie to a new server it should only be fair that players currently on Stormhammer should have the option to move a single character per account to Firiona Vie if they choose to do so.  We have been loyal to Stormhammer and the higher ups have taken this great server away from us and pretty much taken a huge dump on our heads.   Both the players and our great GM staff. &lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt; &lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;I only want the equal chance that people should be able to move to Firiona Vie as I had the chance to move to another server instead of going back to Firiona Vie.  That would be the only action that would be fair.  If they allowed me off of Firiona Vie breaking their own rules then people here should have the chance to be able to transfer there if they choose to do so.  I  am not here to start trouble as I have the upmost respect for Lydrea, Anahadu, and Deodan , but I feel people should have the option of going to Firiona if they choose as I had the same option of not going back to Firiona Vie.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt; &lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Thanks,&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Thomas Ruffin&lt;/div&gt;</description>
