      <description>&lt;DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;&lt;SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: navy; FONT-FAMILY: Arial"&gt;&lt;FONT color=#cccccc&gt;Characters currently on Stormhammer that were created on Firiona Vie will need to contact &lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;A href="mailto:legendsmoveback@soe.sony.com" target=_blank&gt;&lt;FONT color=#ffcc00&gt;legendsmoveback@soe.sony.com&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/A&gt;&lt;FONT color=#cccccc&gt; to arrange for their character to be moved back to Firiona Vie.&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
